{"tid":1243744,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[無人理]生日派對零宣傳！SJ利特無奈訴「誰都不幹活」","createTime":"2019-06-19T15:00:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T01:30:14.000Z","uid":188406,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ea47263b82c7bac829295f2dc25ac353013ad1bf","tid":1243744,"uid":188406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:00:49.000Z","msg":"即將在來臨的7月1日度過37歲（韓國年齡算法）生日的Super Junior隊長利特，將會在生日的前一天，也就是6月30日舉辦與粉絲一起慶祝的生日派對。沒想到SJ所屬的獨立工作室廠牌Label SJ到18日為止，都沒有進行任何宣傳，就連售票詳情，派對舉辦日期和地點都沒有對外發佈，讓「壽星」利特很是無奈，只能透過個人IG自行宣傳。<br />\n從利特的話語中可以看出，他一直都在等公司開啟宣傳，但距離派對還有約一個多星期，仍然沒有任何售票和宣傳工作，利特只好自己宣佈消息，艾古呀，真的是滿滿的無奈啊！粉絲們見到利特的PO文後，都留言表示憤怒和心疼，怒批公司實在是太過分了！<br />\n終於，在利特「訴苦」的PO文公開幾小時後，公司員工似乎「上班」了，在SJ的各大官網和SNS上傳了利特生日派對的宣傳海報，並公開售票詳情。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sarangoppa.com/1/4326/%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A5%E6%B4%BE%E5%B0%8D%E9%9B%B6%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3SJ%E5%88%A9%E7%89%B9%E7%84%A1%E5%A5%88%E8%A8%B4%E8%AA%B0%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E5%B9%B9%E6%B4%BB%E5%B9%BE.html?fbclid=IwAR19C_BuLyc5B7KkXOeAqevSKdpakxcMFdRdBsAeISx_IClLOMURnsBRmEk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sarangoppa.com%2F1%2F4326%2F%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%259B%25B6%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%2582%25B3SJ%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%2589%25B9%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25A5%2588%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E8%25AA%25B0%25E9%2583%25BD%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B9%25B9%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%25B9%25BE.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR19C_BuLyc5B7KkXOeAqevSKdpakxcMFdRdBsAeISx_IClLOMURnsBRmEk&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyuzBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=078e64cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sarangoppa.com/1/4326/%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A5%E6%B4%BE%E5%B0%8D%E9%9B%B6%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3SJ%E5%88%A9%E7%89%B9%E7%84%A1%E5%A5%88%E8%A8%B4%E8%AA%B0%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E5%B9%B9%E6%B4%BB%E5%B9%BE.html?fbclid=IwAR19C_BuLyc5B7KkXOeAqevSKdpakxcMFdRdBsAeISx_IClLOMURnsBRmEk</a><br />\n好`慘,特特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664e